                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-23-defend306 t17850914-23-punish112"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice ASHURST.</p>
